rows.label: tev056601_SEL0031

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Not easy to survive on harsh planet like Mira,
so Moimoi dedicate much of his life to cultivating
ancestral Nopon technology.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0002
rows.name:
Technology of human friends not too shabby either,
but Moimoi and Nopon crew are true champions of
technological arena![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0003
rows.name:
...What? Earth friend does not believe Moimoi?
Meh! Friend should check out selection of wares at
Nopon Commerce Guild before running mouth![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0004
rows.name:
Every super cool weapon on sale is packed to brim
with crickly-crackly thermal energy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0005
rows.name:
Monsters like jacul HATE the crickly-crackly,
so Nopon weapon really hits spot. Friend will be
thanking Nopon everywhere with tears in eyes![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Informant Cheche told Moimoi all about city.
That is why Moimoi came.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0011
rows.name:
But many alien races and incredible inventions of
city STILL blew tuft off Moimoi![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0012
rows.name:
In Armory Alley, friend can easily buy all sorts of
amazing machines and junk![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0013
rows.name:
Moimoi is going to get big brotherpon Muimui to
buy LOTS of things for research.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Moimoi and brotherpon Muimui are very first Nopon
to join BLADE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0019
rows.name: Pretty amazing, right? Want to shake hand of hero?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0020
rows.name:
Moimoi has made many inventions and none have
been hits. But friend just wait![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG0021
rows.name:
Next invention is going to be knock out of park for
BLADE adventurers. Moimoi want to make life easier
for friends everywhere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1001
rows.name:
Moimoi heard really loud BANG BANG noise and
came running. Thought there might be fireworks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1002
rows.name:
But sound was actually just Ganglion machines trying
to blow up city. Friends were totally surrounded![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1003
rows.name:
Moimoi and Muimui watched whole shebang from
relative safety of mountaintop.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1004
rows.name:
Then, after surprising victory of friends, Moimoi and
Muimui ran onto battlefield and looted Ganglion
wreckage![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1005
rows.name:
Many thanks, by the way. Hard work of friend helped
Moimoi and Muimui get hands on lots of supplies
for inventions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1010
rows.name:
Muimui is doing great with new job!
Every now and then Moimoi gets message.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1011
rows.name:
Brotherpon still not manage to find Sword of
Legendaryness...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1012
rows.name:
But Muimui did stumble on rare flower called sona
herb at Northpointe Cove![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1013
rows.name:
Moimoi very proud of brother for turning into such
kick-butt BLADE.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1018
rows.name:
Moimoi is also BLADE, and cannot simply stand in
shadow of brotherpon forever![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1019
rows.name:
So Moimoi choose to gear up, get out there,
and show Ganglion baddies who is boss![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1020
rows.name:
Unfortunately, three seconds into battle, big giant
controlled by Ryyz kicked Moimoi out of city like
little furry soccer ball.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1021
rows.name:
Moimoi had horrible time out there while waiting
for bruises and sprains and muscle pain to heal...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG1022
rows.name:
If only Moimoi had some kind of hyper armor capable
of withstanding any attack... MEEEEEEEEEHHHH!
Moimoi just stumble on new invention![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG2001
rows.name:
Moimoi decided to take closer look at legendary toy
sword brought home by brotherpon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG2002
rows.name:
Turn out there is button in middle that causes crest on
sword to make flashies![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG2003
rows.name:
...Market price still very low, but it look so cool!
Great Nopon ancestors think of everything when
designing official merchandise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG3001
rows.name:
Moimoi decided to try cleaning ears with Earwax-
Remover of Legendaryness brotherpon found.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG3002
rows.name:
SOOOOOO GOOOOOOD! Meeeeeh...
Like ears died and went off to clean-ear heaven.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG3003
rows.name:
Talk about masterwork of engineering!
Great ancestors really knew what Nopon look for
in ear-hygiene product.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG3004
rows.name:
Might be while before Sword of Legendaryness turns
up, so Moimoi definitely considering mass-producing
earwax-remover instead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG3005
rows.name:
Every Nopon in Nopondom will want one!
Moimoi going to make credits hand over fist.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4001
rows.name:
Friend must wage epic deadly battle to get back real
bodies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4002
rows.name:
Moimoi and brotherpon will stay in city and keep
everyone nice and safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4003
rows.name:
Do not worry! Moimoi and Muimui are BLADE
veterans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4004
rows.name:
No problem laying waste to mob of blatta or terebra.
Moimoi will destroy them all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4005
rows.name:
...Hmm? What about Prone? Friend must be kidding!
Moimoi not have death wish or something.
Moimoi not want to get EATEN![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4010
rows.name:
Moimoi just about ready to go forward with plan to
mass-produce Earwax-Remover of Legendaryness that
brotherpon Muimui find.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4011
rows.name:
When Moimoi provide prototype sample to Cheche,
it must have felt good, because Cheche shout "Hoy!"
at top of lungs![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4012
rows.name:
Very possible earwax-remover will become smash hit
and sell like wildfire among Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4013
rows.name:
Moimoi need to make it up to brotherpon for eating
every last scrap of food...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4014
rows.name:
So once Moimoi basically printing money,
Moimoi will repay brother. No worries![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4019
rows.name:
Guess what? Moimoi invent special hyper armor for
Nopon that can withstand any impact.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4020
rows.name:
Once finer details are worked out, Moimoi planning
to put hyper armor on and go help brother Muimui
with missions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4021
rows.name:
Moimoi has big plans to bust tuft as BLADE and
achieve ultimate Curator dream of filling up entire
Collectopedia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_MSG4022
rows.name:
How does Collectopedia of friend look at moment?
Friend seems pretty good at collecting, actually.
Maybe friend can give Moimoi few tips?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056601_SEL0032
rows.name:
Ask Moimoi about the battle
at the Lifehold Core.
